★ Browns x Duran Lantink ★⠀
. ⠀
British high-end retailer @brownsfashion introduces a conscious collection with @duranlantinkyo – shortlisted in the 2019 edition of the LVMH Prize – as part of their new Conscious category. In the new category Browns will bring designers that “integrate the circular economy into their business and work with sustainable materials.”⠀
. ⠀
Credit: @hypebeast⠀
. ⠀
#lvmhprize #lvmhprize2020 #sustainability #brownsfashion

★ Vintage ★⠀
. ⠀
“People are drawn to vintage because of the stories there. You know that it had a life before and you can feel that. Its rarity is a huge aspect of why we have certain clients that shop our brand and why a lot of people that buy vintage also buy us. You have one and that’s it.”⠀
. ⠀
@bode – finalist of LVMH Prize 2019 – talks about her love of vintage in an interview with @thelastmagazine.⠀
. ⠀
#lvmhprize #lvmhprize2020 #sustainability
